{
  "stem": "27340.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Uh, uh, I think it's fair to say I was impressed by the paramilitarism of the Hitler Youth.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We lived, before we moved into my grandfather's house, in a flat that was not too far away from an old, uh, uh military barracks that was continued to be used by the German army.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And very often, that parade, that was a, a cavalry unit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they paraded around on horseback.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had a terrific band.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was always impressed by the, by the, the big drummer who had these kettle drums on either side of the horse, and the way he was waving around with his, uh, drum sticks, as they were.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Uh, the military music impressed me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The precision impressed me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course, that was translated later on into the Hitler youth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They marched around in hordes and in groups and columns and, uh, in, uh, military units.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I felt sad to some considerable extent that I was not in the position to join them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I would have been quite happy in, under such circumstances.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The precision, the discipline, the military, um, splendor, you know [LAUGHS], italics, if I can call it that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That, Of course, applies to all military units, not only of the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I mean, th-- that was the only thing I had ever seen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And yes, I, I often felt what a pity that I couldn't join this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there was, of course, nothing equivalent amongst the Jewish youth for this type of thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was an organization similar to Ajax in this country to which my father belonged as well, which was the Association of Jewish Front Line Soldiers, I think would be the correct translation, the Reichsbund judischer Frontsoldaten, as it was called in German.",
      "word_count": 43
    }
  ],
